records.name: Jw Marriott Maldives Resort & Spa

descriptions.direction: Located in Vagaru, JW Marriott Maldives Resort & Spa is on a private beach. Local points of interest include Velaa Private Island and Orimasvaru Island Pier.
descriptions.general: This sophisticated resort is set in Shaviyani Atoll. The premises count 60 welcoming accommodation units. In addition, Wi-Fi access is offered at the resort. The reception is open 24/7. Thanks to the leisure options offered at this establishment, guests may enjoy a fun-filled experience. All guests staying at this property may indulge in the health and wellness treatments available on the premises. The property's dining offer has a reputation for excellent cuisine and top-notch service. Hotel check out not allowed on 31st December 2023, 1 and 2 January 2024.
